1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,470
What's the matter, young man? What are you doing here?
你怎么了  年轻人  你在这里干嘛呢

2
00:00:04,520 --> 00:00:07,180
I'm looking for my little kitten.
我在找我的小猫咪

3
00:00:07,230 --> 00:00:10,220
He's missing. Should I call the police?
他失踪了  我要报警吗

4
00:00:10,280 --> 00:00:15,280
For your kitten? I think I can help. What does he look like?
为了你的小猫吗  我想我可以帮忙  他长什么样

5
00:00:15,320 --> 00:00:22,170
Mmm... he has beautiful eyes. He's all white but black on the top of his head.
恩  他的眼睛很漂亮  他除了头顶是黑色的以外其余都是白色的

6
00:00:22,230 --> 00:00:25,370
I guess you are feeling very sad.
我猜你肯定很伤心

7
00:00:25,450 --> 00:00:30,040
Yes. My uncle gave the kitten to me only yesterday.
是的  我叔叔昨天才把他送给我

8
00:00:30,120 --> 00:00:35,600
I hope he's not out there on the street. There are so many cars and buses there.
我希望他没有跑到街上去  那里可有很多的汽车和公交车

9
00:00:35,640 --> 00:00:38,910
Perhaps he's just having fun in the garden.
也许他只是在公园里玩呢

10
00:00:38,960 --> 00:00:42,500
Would you please look for him together with me?
你能帮我一起找吗

11
00:00:42,590 --> 00:00:44,950
Sure. Let's go.
当然了  我们走

